000Z","msg":"夜訓又早起唔到 搞到成個行程推遲哂<br />\n<br />\nPLAN行程時 揀埋哂D山旮旯咁遠的景點 (成個區一左一右<br />\n<br />\n揀景點就咁掉條LINK出黎叫你睇 根本睇完個TOPIC無理過個餡 <br />\n都算 我忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少叫有參與過 但好多時打開都係廣告垃圾文<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPLAN好行程/搭車資料之後 根本無記過入腦 到地之後矇乘乘完全唔知做乜 淨係識得呆企&amp;跟自己尾 結果我要照顧埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到外地玩緊仍然不停同香港朋友傾計whatsapp<br />\n大佬 你係同緊我去旅行 唔係同電話入面果個去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02fc14567a655ff190c00ea9e34500cb1a0dc70","tid":917072,"uid":57252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:35:51.000Z","msg":"留名學旅行"},{"pid":"ca6096f018c6c65168a866196ce6c583122d2ce6","tid":917072,"uid":112237,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafd14d25e6461d7972b5097e3989dbc85df0e81","tid":917072,"uid":112237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca6096f018c6c65168a866196ce6c583122d2ce6","tid":917072,"uid":112237,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04656b85ae289cc630f0bb127e381e7788ced761","tid":917072,"uid":219244,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"呢個post真係月經<br />\n<br />\n好憎人plan行程又唔出現，約佢出嚟傾一次好似要求佢咁，同佢講番個行程又唔上心<br />\n去到淨係識得問問問，帶漏野又問我做咩唔同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗，我咪講過俾你知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，有啲地方叫咗佢去之前得閒睇吓資料<br />\n如果唔係去到真係乜都唔知企係度<br />\n<br />\n結果佢睇都冇睇過，去到又叫我同佢介紹